assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) (cavlc_fsm_::rst_n ##2 true) |-> cavlc_fsm_::idle);
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) (!cavlc_fsm_::idle ##1 true) |-> cavlc_fsm_::idle);
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) ((cavlc_fsm_::state == 0) ##4 true) |-> cavlc_fsm_::idle);
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) (cavlc_fsm_::rst_n ##3 true) |-> (cavlc_fsm_::state == 1));
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) (!cavlc_fsm_::idle ##4 true) |-> cavlc_fsm_::idle);
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) (cavlc_fsm_::rst_n ##1 true) |-> cavlc_fsm_::idle);
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) ((cavlc_fsm_::state == 0) ##3 true) |-> (cavlc_fsm_::state == 1));
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) (!cavlc_fsm_::idle ##2 true) |-> cavlc_fsm_::idle);
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) (!cavlc_fsm_::idle ##1 true) |-> (cavlc_fsm_::state == 1));
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) (!cavlc_fsm_::idle ##3 true) |-> cavlc_fsm_::idle);
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) ((cavlc_fsm_::state == 0) ##4 true) |-> (cavlc_fsm_::state == 1));
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) (cavlc_fsm_::rst_n ##4 true) |-> (cavlc_fsm_::state == 1));
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) (!cavlc_fsm_::idle ##3 true) |-> (cavlc_fsm_::state == 1));
assert property(@(posedge cavlc_fsm_::clk) ((cavlc_fsm_::state == 0) ##3 true) |-> cavlc_fsm_::idle);
